<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Dashboard' }) %>

<h1>Review queues</h1>
<p class="muted">Pick a queue to walk pending items.</p>

<%- include('partials/help', {
  title: 'three things the pipeline can flag for you',
  open: true,
  body: `
    <p>The automated pipeline classifies and canonicalises every record. When it
    can't, the record lands in one of these three queues:</p>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Queue</th><th>Why records arrive</th><th>What you do</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><strong>Reviews</strong></td><td>Classifier picked a SOC but flagged the pick as suspicious.</td><td>Accept · Override · Reject</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Quarantine</strong></td><td>Classifier refused to pick, or validation failed at ingest.</td><td>Assign SOC manually · Drop</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Unresolved</strong></td><td>Entity-resolution layers (FEIN / pg_trgm / pgvector) all missed.</td><td>Merge into existing canonical · Create new · Reject</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>Every action is a transactional write. The merge/create actions on the
    Unresolved queue cascade — one click backfills <code>canonical_employer_id</code>
    on every matching <code>lca_records</code> row. Take a moment before each click.</p>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/anthropics/lca-normalization-engine/blob/main/apps/operator-ui/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Full manual →</a></p>
  `
}) %>

<div class="queue-grid">
  <a class="queue-card" href="/reviews">
    <h2>Reviews</h2>
    <div class="big-number"><%= counts.reviews.toLocaleString() %></div>
    <p>lca_records flagged <code>requires_review = true</code> (short-title LLM picks, low-confidence Stage 2).</p>
  </a>
  <a class="queue-card" href="/quarantine">
    <h2>Quarantine</h2>
    <div class="big-number"><%= counts.quarantine.toLocaleString() %></div>
    <p>staging.quarantine_records — LLM-refused residue. Manual SOC assignment or drop.</p>
  </a>
  <a class="queue-card" href="/unresolved">
    <h2>Unresolved employers</h2>
    <div class="big-number"><%= counts.unresolved.toLocaleString() %></div>
    <p>staging.unresolved_employers — entity-resolution misses. Merge into existing canonical or create new.</p>
  </a>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
